{
  "$description": "DepoStack brand tokens mapped to DepoAudio's semantic layer. Plum = ink (inverts to cream in dark), cream/night = surfaces, gold = accent/CTA (never text on light — active states use plum). Every text token meets WCAG AAA (7:1); status colors are the brand hues deepened to clear 7:1 as text on their surfaces, and destructive is dark in light / light in dark so it is AAA both as text and as a fill. The one exception is the plum-on-gold CTA fill (5.9:1), a documented brand exception. Color $values are `H S% L%` (consumed via hsl(var(--token))) unless prefixed `color-` (full paint values for SVG/box-shadow). Regenerate CSS with `npm run tokens`.",
